Amber Heard is back in the news. The actress who has been embroiled in back-to-back controversies may soon have some good news to share with her fans. The only project he has on his next schedule is Aquaman 2 from the DCEU. However, there have been several headlines about decreasing or increasing the actress' screen time. But it looks like Marvel has their eyes set on her. Even though there have been deceptive conversations that she could be fired from producing the DCEU for failing a medical exam, it seems Amber still has reason to rejoice.
